      <title>拜登的司法部反垄断负责人让特朗普创纪录的垄断案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-s-doj-antitrust-chief-leaves-trump-record-monopoly-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府目前针对涉嫌垄断的未决案件数量，比 20 世纪初反垄断法首次通过后任何时候都要多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-s-doj-antitrust-chief-leaves-trump-record-monopoly-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
