    <item>
      <title>加拿大扩大空中边境监视以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/canada-expands-aerial-border-surveillance-to-pacify-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大正在部署所谓的“空中情报工作组”，这是新一轮 13 亿加元（9.08 亿美元）计划的一部分，旨在解决美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对移民和芬太尼穿越北部边境的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/canada-expands-aerial-border-surveillance-to-pacify-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行的莫伊尼汉表示，监管机构需要“冷静审视”银行规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bofa-s-moynihan-says-regulators-need-sober-look-at-bank-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司首席执行官布莱恩·莫伊尼汉表示，监管机构需要重新评估并放宽为银行制定的规则，这可能是特朗普政府上台后银行业面临的最大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bofa-s-moynihan-says-regulators-need-sober-look-at-bank-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大臣近期游说反对对华企业实施严厉限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-minister-recently-lobbied-against-tough-china-business-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政部一名大臣游说前保守党政府，要求金融业放松对中国商业活动的限制，凸显出基尔·史塔默政府在新的间谍丑闻爆发期间支持与北京保持联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-minister-recently-lobbied-against-tough-china-business-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将于未来几天宣布对中国半导体进行调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-to-announce-chinese-semiconductor-probe-in-coming-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的政府将在未来几天对中国半导体展开贸易调查，此举旨在减少对美国官员认为构成国家安全风险的技术的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-to-announce-chinese-semiconductor-probe-in-coming-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:28:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长亚当斯未能使联邦贿赂指控被驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/nyc-mayor-adams-fails-to-get-federal-bribery-charge-thrown-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯未能使针对他的贿赂指控被撤销，这将导致他于 4 月接受一场备受瞩目的审判，尽管他正准备竞选连任，但他很可能会在审判中面对针对他的全部五项指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/nyc-mayor-adams-fails-to-get-federal-bribery-charge-thrown-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国会考虑因社会问题削弱卢拉的财政计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-congress-mulls-watering-down-lula-s-spending-cut-plan-on-social-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责向国会提交新版法案的议员表示，由于担心社会福利改革将损害穷人的利益，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的支出削减计划的一个关键部分将被淡化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-congress-mulls-watering-down-lula-s-spending-cut-plan-on-social-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 19:57:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登的液化天然气出口研究给特朗普带来“障碍”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-releases-study-of-lng-exports-that-could-hamstring-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周二发布了一项重要研究，这可能会使当选总统唐纳德·特朗普迅速批准更多液化天然气出口的计划变得复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-releases-study-of-lng-exports-that-could-hamstring-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>支持加密货币的议员希尔关注数字资产和银行监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/pro-crypto-french-hill-eyes-digital-asset-banking-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在共和党准备于明年 1 月统一控制华盛顿之际，负责监督金融监管机构和华尔街的众议院强大委员会即将迎来一位新主席，其首要任务是讨论加密货币和银行业放松管制问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/pro-crypto-french-hill-eyes-digital-asset-banking-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 18:55:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
